englishTranslationText:
And	 We	 admitted	 them	 into	 Our	 mercy;	
indeed	they	are	among	those	who	deserve	
Our	proximity.

And	 they	will	not	hear its	 faintest	sound;	
and	 they	 will	 forever	 abide	 in	 whatever	
their	hearts	desire.

They	 worship	 such,	 beside	 Allah,	 which	
neither	 harms	 them	 nor	 benefits	 them;	
this	only	is	the	extreme	error.

And	 they	 were	 guided	 to	 sacred	 speech;	
and	they	were	shown	the	path	of	the	Most	
Praiseworthy.
